i-agents/main/Labfiles/01-agent-fundamentals/Expenses_Policy.docx" target=
=3D"_blank" aria-label=3D"(opens a new window)">Expenses_policy.docx</a> fr=
om <code class=3D"prettyprint prettyprinted" tabindex=3D"0" style=3D""><spa=
n class=3D"pln">https</span><span class=3D"pun">:</span><span class=3D"com"=
>//raw.githubusercontent.com/MicrosoftLearning/mslearn-ai-agents/main/Labfi=
les/01-agent-fundamentals/Expenses_Policy.docx</span></code> and save it lo=
cally. This document contains details of the expenses policy for the fictio=
nal Contoso corporation.</p></li>
<li class=3D"task-list-item" id=3D"taskIndex11"><p><label class=3D"checkbox=
"><input type=3D"checkbox" aria-labelledby=3D"taskIndex11"><span></span></l=
abel>Return to the browser tab where you have the playground open for your =
expense agent.</p></li>
<li class=3D"task-list-item" id=3D"taskIndex12"><p><label class=3D"checkbox=
"><input type=3D"checkbox" aria-labelledby=3D"taskIndex12"><span></span></l=
abel>Set the <strong>Instructions</strong> to:</p>
<pre><div class=3D"codeTitle"><span class=3D"title">prompt</span><span clas=
s=3D"title"><span class=3D"type-code-block">Type</span><span class=3D"copy-=
code-block">Copy</span></span></div><code class=3D"prompt language-prompt p=
rettyprint prettyprinted" tabindex=3D"0" style=3D""><span class=3D"typ">You=
</span><span class=3D"pln"> are an AI assistant </span><span class=3D"kwd">=
for</span><span class=3D"pln"> corporate expenses</span><span class=3D"pun"=
>.</span><span class=3D"pln">
</span><span class=3D"typ">You</span><span class=3D"pln"> answer questions =
about expenses based on the expenses policy data</span><span class=3D"pun">=
.</span><span class=3D"pln">
</span><span class=3D"typ">If</span><span class=3D"pln"> a user wants to su=
bmit an expense claim</span><span class=3D"pun">,</span><span class=3D"pln"=
> you </span><span class=3D"kwd">get</span><span class=3D"pln"> their email=
 address</span><span class=3D"pun">,</span><span class=3D"pln"> a descripti=
on </span><span class=3D"kwd">of</span><span class=3D"pln"> the claim</span=
><span class=3D"pun">,</span><span class=3D"pln"> </span><span class=3D"kwd=
">and</span><span class=3D"pln"> the amount to be claimed </span><span clas=
s=3D"kwd">and</span><span class=3D"pln"> write the claim details to a text =
file that the user can download</span><span class=3D"pun">.</span></code></=
pre>
