d@contoso</span><span class=3D"pun">.</span><span class=3D"pln">com</span><=
/code>. The agent should acknowledge the response and request the remaining=
 information required for the expense claim (description and amount)</p></l=
i>
<li class=3D"task-list-item" id=3D"taskIndex24"><p><label class=3D"checkbox=
"><input type=3D"checkbox" aria-labelledby=3D"taskIndex24"><span></span></l=
abel>Submit a prompt that describes the claim and the amount; for example, =
<code class=3D"prettyprint prettyprinted" tabindex=3D"0" style=3D""><span c=
